Get the center of the chunk according to the zone (so center of the 10x10

methods.name: initAllRVSMapChance
methods.notes: We init a map with every possible stories for this zone

RVSBurntCar.notes: Just a burnt car with 0, 1 or 2 burnt corpses near it

constructors.notes: Vehicle alone, corpse not so far from the car's front with blood trail

RVSChangingTire.notes: Good car with a couple changing its tire

RVSConstructionSite.notes: Van with a sewer hole & road cones around it, some construction worker and a foreman + some tools in ground

RVSCrashHorde.notes: Car crashed with quite some zombies around it

RVSFlippedCrash.notes: Flipped car with bodies & blood near it, can be burnt

RVSPoliceBlockade.notes: Police barricading a road, 2 police cars, some zombies police

RVSPoliceBlockadeShooting.notes: Police barricading a road, 2 police cars, some zombies police with guns/rifle, dead corpses around

RVSUtilityVehicle.notes: An utility vehicle (mccoys, fire dept, police, ranger, postal..) with corresponding outfit zeds and sometimes tools
